---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import HeroSection from "../../components/HeroSection.astro";
import VisionStatement from "../../components/VisionStatement.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="Our Ambition | Green Orbit Digital"
  description="Discover Green Orbit Digital’s ambition to accelerate sustainable growth across the space, technology, and climate sectors through responsible innovation and data-driven strategy."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="py-8">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <HeroSection
      title="Our Ambition"
      description="We accelerate responsible innovation across the space and sustainability sectors—helping organisations turn complex ideas into measurable impact."
    />

    <!-- Vision Statement -->
    <section class="py-12 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <VisionStatement />
    </section>

    <!-- Introduction -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-white py-12">
      <p>
        At Green Orbit Digital, our ambition is to help organisations unlock the full value of space-enabled 
        innovation and sustainability-led strategy. By bridging emerging technologies with real-world adoption, 
        we empower teams to communicate their impact clearly, build trust, and grow responsibly.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our work sits at the intersection of digital strategy, the space sector, and climate innovation—driving 
        progress that is transparent, inclusive, and aligned with a more sustainable future.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Solving What Matters -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-primary-500">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">

        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 2l7 4v6c0 5-3 9-7 10-4-1-7-5-7-10V6l7-4z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Solving What Matters</h2>
        </div>

        <p>
          We focus on the challenges shaping the next decade—climate resilience, data transparency, sustainable 
          growth, and the responsible use of space-enabled insights. Through hands-on collaboration, we help 
          organisations de-risk new ideas, communicate complex innovation, and turn advanced capability into 
          measurable outcomes.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>De-risking early adoption of emerging digital and space-based technologies</li>
          <li>Strengthening long-term sustainability and ESG alignment</li>
          <li>Bringing clarity and credibility to climate and innovation storytelling</li>
          <li>Building trust through science-backed data and transparent reporting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Partnering for Progress -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">

        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Partnering for Progress</h2>
        </div>

        <p>
          Progress is collaborative. We work with startups, public-sector bodies, research institutions, 
          corporates, and investors to drive responsible adoption of digital, sustainability, and space-enabled 
          solutions. Our goal is to ensure every partner moves forward with clarity, confidence, and purpose.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Supporting growth across the UK’s space and climate-tech clusters</li>
          <li>Strengthening local, regional, and national innovation ecosystems</li>
          <li>Translating complex research and policy into accessible public understanding</li>
          <li>Guiding teams through investment readiness, ESG proof points, and digital maturity</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Challenging Purposefully -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-primary-500">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">

        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 5v14"/>
            <path d="M18 13l-6 6l-6-6"/>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Challenging Purposefully</h2>
        </div>

        <p>
          We believe in challenging assumptions to unlock better outcomes. Purposeful challenge helps teams think 
          differently, adopt sustainable practices, and make meaningful progress—grounded in scientific thinking 
          and strategic clarity.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Encouraging evidence-led strategy and transparent communication</li>
          <li>Aligning growth with environmental responsibility</li>
          <li>Refining messaging to increase credibility and stakeholder confidence</li>
          <li>Embedding sustainability and data integrity across digital initiatives</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Intersection of Space, Sustainability & Digital -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">

        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
            <path d="M19.4 15a8 8 0 1 0-3.4 3.4"/>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">At the Intersection of Space, Sustainability & Digital</h2>
        </div>

        <p>
          Our work spans three interconnected domains that define the modern innovation landscape:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Space & Earth Observation</strong> – satellite data for climate and sustainability insights.</li>
          <li><strong>Digital Strategy</strong> – SEO, content, and performance analysis with measurable results.</li>
          <li><strong>Sustainability & Climate Innovation</strong> – alignment with net-zero goals, ESG frameworks, and scientific evidence.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Impact-Driven Support -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-primary-500">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">

        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M3 3v18h18"/>
            <path d="M7 14l3-3l4 4l5-5"/>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Impact-Driven, Hands-On Support</h2>
        </div>

        <p>
          Our ambition is grounded in meaningful, measurable outcomes. We provide the tools, insight, and 
          strategic direction needed to turn complex innovation into real-world impact.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Digital and sustainability audits aligned with sector needs</li>
          <li>Sustainability-led content and data storytelling</li>
          <li>Thought-leadership built from climate and space insights</li>
          <li>Support for launches, investment rounds, and scale-up milestones</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <!-- Closing Section -->
  <section class="w-full bg-secondary-500 py-16 text-white text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Building a Future-Ready, Sustainable Space Economy</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-200 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Our ambition is to help organisations harness innovation responsibly and at scale—creating a greener, 
      more resilient, and more connected future. Together, we can strengthen the UK’s leadership in sustainable 
      space, digital transformation, and climate innovation.
    </p>
    <a 
      href="/contact"
      class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-lg transition"
    >
      Start a Conversation
    </a>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>